    public class QueryIterHashLeftJoin_Left
extends AbstractIterHashJoin
    Hash left join. This code materializes the left hand side into a probe table then hash joins from the right. See QueryIterHashLeftJoin_Right for one that uses the right hand side to make the probe table.
